member.name: TF_PROPERTYVAL
member.summary: The TF_PROPERTYVAL structure contains property value data. This structure is used with the method.

member.name: TF_PROPERTYVAL.guidId
member.summary: A GUID that identifies the property type. This can be a custom identifier or one of the predefined property identifiers.

member.name: TF_PROPERTYVAL.varValue
member.summary: A VARIANT that contains the value of the property specified by guidId. The user must know the type and format of this data.
